room_title: Escape room "T.I.T.U.S." by Perplexity Games in Cleveland
room_description:
Humanity hovers on the brink of a new world order. T.I.T.U.S., an advanced artificial intelligence, has gone rogue and is rapidly hijacking global communication, defense, energy and transportation systems. Shut it down, or prepare to serve the machines.
There are two identical rooms available at the location, both for 2-5 players. Groups of 6 and more people will be divided and compete against each other to see who escapes first.
